    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【故事】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338380/extras/57c76f8bc306c3fbcada2fe4bd8a8a06.avif?t=1766031425\" width=600 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——为了那名求救的少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >庇护孩童的温柔神明——雪音。<br>在她居住的神社里，响起了少女呼救的声音。<br>那道从充满邪恶气息的异空间里所传来的声音，让雪音不顾危险，纵身跃入其中。<br>可怕的邪祟限制了神力，但雪音还是为了少女探索起被诅咒的宅邸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为什麽这栋宅邸会被诅咒呢？<br>求救的少女又身在何方？<br>——雪音是否能够解开邪祟宅邸之谜，从中救出少女呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【玩法介绍】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338380/extras/f18fbb8eb344616e105e78d6ed89f712.poster.avif?t=1766031425\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338380/extras/f18fbb8eb344616e105e78d6ed89f712.webm?t=1766031425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338380/extras/f18fbb8eb344616e105e78d6ed89f712.mp4?t=1766031425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时需要组合道具、解开谜团、避开陷阱及威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338380/extras/84b5b1384381b9ada966d283b14976f9.avif?t=1766031425\" width=600 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了前进，帮助无法成佛的幽灵也相当重要。<br>或许还会因此获得攻略所需的道具喔。 <br> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【角色介绍】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338380/extras/2024ccbfa5443cc17c28d075e4665945.avif?t=1766031425\" width=300 height=371 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▲ 雪音</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守护孩童、相当灵验的温柔神明。<br>长期担任神明，但仍有些孩子气。最喜欢吃泡芙。<br>听见少女求救的声音，她明知危险，却还是纵身跃入邪祟的世界里――</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338380/extras/e0e54e9c009b253de8407355641bc7b3.avif?t=1766031425\" width=300 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▲ 少女</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被囚禁在邪祟宅邸中的少女。<br>丧失五感，即使与之交谈也不会出现任何反应。<br>似乎仅剩内心尚存，像是依赖雪音一般紧跟着她。<br>是介于灵体和肉体之间的存在。似乎出生于古代——</p>",
